name: Wrapped USDC
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Wrapped USDC on Stacks (xUSD) is a 1:1 equivalent of USDC on the Stacks network.

Wrapped.com lets investors use their digital assets to lend, borrow, and trade on all major DeFi platforms.

Wrapped.com is a collaboration of Tokensoft Inc. with custodians and other financial institutions. Tokensoft provides the technology layer via Wrapped.com that allows users to wrap their USDC into xUSD.
